MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-164. Watson v. Miami Cty. Mun. Court.

Miami County, No. 95CA71. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Miami County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective April 29,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.

Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., dissent and would deny the application as untimely.
